## Swift  
2014-06-09

### 
[iBook](https://itunes.apple.com/us/book/the-swift-programming-language/id881256329?mt=11)

IDE Xcode 6 Beta

### Hello World
```swift
    println("Hello World!")
```
### 2014-06-09
(let)(var)\()Swift var numValue = 123, strValue = "abc"

func:
```swift
    func hello(name: String, day: String) -> String {
         return "Hello \(name), Today is \(day) !"
    }
```

```swift
    func sumOf(numbers: Int...) -> Int {
        var sum = 0
        for number in numbers {
            sum += number
        }
        return sum
    }
    sumOf()
    sumOf(42, 597, 12)
```
 Weather App 

### 2014-06-10
Weather AppDemoJSONAPI

    NSJSONSerialization

Interview

[GitBook Swift](http://numbbbbb.github.io/the-swift-programming-language-in-chinese/)

#### 

ifswitchfor-inforwhiledo-while


```swift
    var optionalString: String? = "Hello"
    optionalString == nil

    var optionalName: String? = "John Appleseed"
    var greeting = "Hello!"
    if let name = optionalName {
        greeting = "Hello, \(name)"
    }
```
if nil false

switch casedefault

 ..  ... 0...10 010100..10 01010

#### 



func->
```swift
    func greet(name: String, day: String) -> String {
        return "Hello \(name), today is \(day)."
    }
    greet("Bob", "Tuesday")
```
